冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e8293772a3d8e0e1955232500360f8fbf4d0546","tid":1192722,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;If you want peace, prepare for war.&rdquo;<br />\nFrom John Wick 3: Parabellum"},{"pid":"b3ce4b73e930a28d65157fe7128b5b8f17614add","tid":1192722,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0676f3dd3b39889fc158e58bbf03b70ef76db39","tid":1192722,"uid":154089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"開台講緊"},{"pid":"d8a1251db77605aa223be8d86d943ad494e468ee","tid":1192722,"uid":203772,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"點解要逼人表態?"},{"pid":"99616327c1ddd830b33e2ec94509a8c8409a10a6","tid":1192722,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p